dct_title_s: Map of the Victoria N'yanza compiled from the original maps of Captn. Speke, Col. Grant & Mr. Stanley, adapted to the recorded observations of Captn. Speke by W. J. Turner
dct_description_sm: Routes of Captn. Speke 1858 & 1862, Col. Grant 1862, and Mr. H. M. Stanley 1875 are shown. Regions surrounding lake are labeled. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 46 (1876), pp. 10-34; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 46 1876
